art of his youth in Normandy; and William claimed to have been nominated by Edward as his successor. Edward was canonized in the 12th century, and came to be venerated throughout Europe as a model of a Christian king."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Laure de Bailleul was born about 1070, in Ponthieu, France. She had at least 1 son with Walter van Peteghem."},"et":{"about 1070–":"umbes 1070–Surnud","1086–Male":"1086–Surnud","1110–1160":"1110–1160","1070–Female":"1070–Surnud","about 1070":"umbes 1070","1110":"1110","1086":"1086","1160":"1160","1070":"1070","Bailleul-en-Vimeu, Ponthieu, France":"Ponthieu, Prantsusmaa","Mortagne Du Nord, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France":"Mortagne-du-Nord, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"about 1070–":"noin 1070–Kuollut","1086–Male":"1086–Kuollut","1110–1160":"1110–1160","1070–Female":"1070–Kuollut","about 1070":"noin 1070","1110":"1110","1086":"1086","1160":"1160","1070":"1070","Bailleul-en-Vimeu, Ponthieu, France":"Ponthieu, Ranska","Mortagne Du Nord, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France":"Mortagne-du-Nord, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, Ranska"},"fr":{"about 1070–":"environ 1070–Décédée","1086–Male":"1086–Décédé","1110–1160":"1110–1160","1070–Female":"1070–Décédée","about 1070":"environ 1070","1110":"1110","1086":"1086","1160":"1160","1070":"1070","Bailleul-en-Vimeu, Ponthieu, France":"Ponthieu, France","Mortagne Du Nord, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France":"Mortagne-du-Nord, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France","lifeSummary":"Laure de Bailleul est née environ 1070, à Ponthieu, France. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Walter van Peteghem."},"de":{"about 1070–":"um 1070–Verstorben","1086–Male":"1086–Verstorben","1110–1160":"1110–1160","1070–Female":"1070–Verstorben","about 1070":"um 1070","1110":"1110","1086":"1086","1160":"1160","1070":"1070","Bailleul-en-Vimeu, Ponthieu, France":"Ponthieu, Frankreich","Mortagne Du Nord, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, France":"Mortagne-du-Nord, Nord, Nord-Pas-de-Calais, Frankreich","lifeSummary":"Laure de Bailleul wur